title: Baolins Speech
author: Dalkorn
pages:
#- Goodbye beautiful New Agora
I will miss all memories here, the people met, and the builds we have shared.
Although I met you about 3 months ago, it will be very sad to see you go.
Through all of the things said, blocks placed, fucks not given...

#- This is family.
And this will be one big family that will stick together.
Goodbye forever, sweet city.
You will be forever miss

~baolin21
#- 